{"name": "xmes-dingtalk-connectflow-sdk", "metadata": {"name": "xmes-dingtalk-connectflow-sdk", "version": "1.0.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests"], "summary": "DingTalk Connection Platform Connection Flow SDK", "upload_time": 1734600969}, "documentation": ["## \u6982\u8ff0\n![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Version-v1.0.0-green)\n![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-%E2%89%A53.9-blue)\n\n`xmes-dingtalk-connectflow-sdk` \u662f\u9489\u9489\u8fde\u63a5\u5e73\u53f0\u81ea\u5efa\u8fde\u63a5\u6d41SDK\uff08\u5411\u7f8e\u800c\u751f\uff09\uff0c\u901a\u8fc7\u8be5\u5de5\u5177\u53ef\u4ee5\u65b9\u4fbf\u5feb\u6377\u7684\u8c03\u7528\u9489\u9489\u7684\u8fde\u63a5\u6d41\u3002\n\n## \u5b89\u88c5\u4f7f\u7528\n```bash\npip install xmes-dingtalk-connectflow-sdk\n```\n\n## \u529f\u80fd\u7279\u5f81\n- \u652f\u6301\u8fde\u63a5\u6d41 `\u591a\u7ef4\u8868CURD_241217`\n\n## \u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5\n### ComplexTable\n\u8be5\u5de5\u5177\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u8fde\u63a5\u6d41 `\u591a\u7ef4\u8868CURD_241217` \u7684\u64cd\u4f5c\u8c03\u7528\u5de5\u5177\u3002\n```python\nfrom DingtalkConnectflowSDK import ComplexTable, GetterFilter, Updater\n\n# \u521d\u59cb\u5316ComplexTable\u5bf9\u8c61\ncomplextable = ComplexTable(flow_url='<\u8fde\u63a5\u6d41\u7684\u540c\u6b65\u534f\u8c03URL>')\n\n# \u83b7\u53d6 Table \u5bf9\u8c61\ntable = complextable.get_table(did='<\u6587\u6863ID>', tid='<\u6570\u636e\u8868ID>')\n\n# \u67e5\u8be2\u6570\u636e\nfilters = [\n    GetterFilter(field='\u6765\u6e90', operator='equal', value=['SDK', 'API'])\n]\nresp = table.get(size=10, fillters=filters)\n\n# \u65b0\u589e\u6570\u636e\nrecords = [\n    {'\u6807\u9898': 'Test Record 1', '\u6765\u6e90': 'SDK},\n    {'\u6807\u9898': 'Test Record 2', '\u6765\u6e90': 'SDK},\n]\nresp = table.add(records)\n\n# \u66f4\u65b0\u6570\u636e\nrecords = [\n    Updater(record_id='<\u8bb0\u5f55ID>', fields={'\u6765\u6e90': 'API'}),\n    Updater(record_id='<\u8bb0\u5f55ID>', fields={'\u6765\u6e90': 'API'}),\n]\nresp = table.update(records)\n\n# \u5220\u9664\u6570\u636e\nrecord_ids = ['<\u8bb0\u5f55ID>', '<\u8bb0\u5f55ID>']\nresp = table.delete(record_ids)\n```"], "modules": [{"name": "DingtalkConnectflowSDk", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "DingtalkConnectflowSDk.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "DingtalkConnectflowSDk.complex_table", "documentation": ["Copyright (c) 2024-now LeslieLiang All rights reserved.\nBuild Date: 2024-12-18\nAuthor: LeslieLiang\nDescription: \u591a\u7ef4\u8868\u8fde\u63a5\u6d41SDK"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "DingtalkConnectflowSDk.complex_table.GetterFilter", "bases": [], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "DingtalkConnectflowSDk.complex_table.GetterFilter.field", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "DingtalkConnectflowSDk.complex_table.GetterFilter.operator", "type": {"name": "Literal", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Literal", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "'equal'", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "'notEqual'", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "'incontain'", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "'notContain'", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "'empty'", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "'notEmpty'", "xref": null, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "DingtalkConnectflowSDk.complex_table.GetterFilter.value", "type": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "